 funds closedend funds etfs and nontraded products highland also offers alternative investments including emerging markets longshort equities real estate and natural resources the members of highland’s real estate team both during their tenure at highland and in their previous roles before joining highland have a long history of investing in real estate and debt related to real estate properties   quarterly results currently unavailable investor faqs  nexpoint residential trust highland capital highland funds affiliates nexpoint advisors nexpoint capital home about us management investment strategy contact us investor relations corporate information corporate profile governance documents committee charting financial materials stock information stock quote historic prices dividends analyst coverage tax information – irs form  sec filings filings insider filings annual report news  presentations event calendar presentations other information investor faqs email notification ir site map news center press releases investor faqs email page × email this page  investor faqs   senders name senders email address recipients name recipients email address enter your comments here   send message required field pdf view print view email alert ir search entire ir site documents press releases ir search  expand all  collapse all where is nexpoint residential trust inc s common stock listed our common stock is listed on nyse under the symbol nxrtfor more detailed stock information please visit our stock quote page does nexpoint residential trust inc  pay a dividend to see a list of our historical dividends please visit our dividends page when did nxrt’s spin off from nhf the company began trading as an independent public company on the new york stock exchange under the ticker symbol nxrt starting april   when does company’s fiscal yearend december  who are the members of nxrt’s management team view our management team who are the members of nxrt’s board of directors view our board o