eal estate investment trust reit that seeks to provide investors access to multifamily real estate investment opportunities in large cities and suburban markets of large cities primarily in the southeastern and southwestern united states we intend to directly or indirectly acquire own operate and selectively develop welllocated core plus multifamily properties with a modest valueadd component the company’s primary investment objectives are  to provide current income for stockholders through the payment of cash distributions  preserve and return stockholders’ capital contributions and  realize capital appreciation on the company’s properties nexpoint multifamily capital trust provides investors an opportunity to invest in the growing american commercial real estate sector more specifically in multifamily real property through a professionally managed alternative investment vehicle managed by an investment firm with approximately  billion in assets under management and a specialized expertise in multifamily real estate investment highland capital fund distributors inc member finra is the dealer manager for the nexpoint multifamily capital trust offering risk factors price – class a share  as of march   price – class t share  news highland capital management announces launch of nontraded product line with affiliate nexpoint advisors posted august   dallas august   – highland capital management lp “highland” a dallasbased investment management firm which together with its affiliates has approximately  billion in assets under management today announced the launch of its nontraded product line with a publiclyregistered business development company bdc nexpoint capital inc  the bdc will be the industry’s first healthcarefocused fund of its kind with a target raise of b… read more  there is no assurance that these objectives will be met the company has no operating history or established financing sources as a result an investment in the company is speculative in addition i